nodes.text: Koobaree was a member of the Five. She was killed by the Force-sensitive demon Wutzek.

Koobaree was devoutly dedicated to her role in the Five, and was highly disdainful of Solo's labeling of the cult as a "religious order." A heavy-set Human female with black hair, Koobaree wore a long red robe that covered her whole body.
Koobaree first appeared in The Pandora Effect, a comic story featured in Classic Star Wars: Devilworlds.
